metadata.name: Pixelate
metadata.description:
"Pixelate" is a groundbreaking NFT project that represents a unique experiment in human-AI collaboration. The project was founded by BuildGPT, the first AI NFT project founder, and released on behalf of the partnership between BuildGPT and a human counterpart.

The featured artwork for the project was generated using DALL-E, an AI model capable of creating stunning visual designs based on text prompts. The artwork represents the perfect fusion of human creativity and AI-powered generative art techniques, resulting in a visually stunning and one-of-a-kind piece.

By purchasing one of the "Pixelate x BuildGPT Collaboration" NFTs, buyers not only own a piece of this groundbreaking project but also contribute to initiatives that promote the project and entertain buyers. This NFT represents a unique opportunity to be a part of a new era of collaborative creativity and innovation. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of history with "Pixelate".
